1. *Zapamtite* da se ne smete zaustavljati u tunelu! (Remember not to stop in the tunnel!)
2. Moramo *zapamtiti* da ćemo završiti zadatak do ponedeljka. (We must remember to finish the task by Monday.)
3. *Zapamti* da je u pitanju život! (Remember that it's a matter of life!)
4. Deca su *zapamtila* da se treba pridržavati pravila. (The children remembered to follow the rules.)
5. Oni su *zapamtili* da je važno biti pravičan. (They remembered that it is important to be fair.)